Notes: UWO ranked 10th in the NCAA Div. III by D3hoops.com...UWST snaps seven-game
losing streak to UWO...UWO falls into a first-place tie in the WIAC standings
with UW-River Falls (four league games left)...UWO gets 17 points and 10
rebounds from Campbell...UWO rallied from 45-33 deficit to take a 48-46 lead.
Game.Officials: Larry Dietz,  Tyler Moy,  Ralph Sirmons
